assets.name: NFT Music Group Membership #00.066
assets.description:
NFT Music Group is a upcoming digital NFT Record Label that represents the NFT music scene.

As the world remains digital; Music Artists, Bands, Producers and DJs are looking for ways to connect and create for their audiences. 
NFT Music Group will provide a new outlet for them with several benefits.
Having a NFT Music Group membership grants you full lifetime access to the future members-only benefits.

There will only be 50.000 NFT Music Group membership given away total.

The members only benefits unlocks the following:

1. Lifetime access to the social media platform
2. Lifetime access to the audio streaming platform
3. All music genres
4. Sell your music
5. Join in on contests
6. Promote your music
7. Reach more fans
8. Network and collabs
9. Link with music managers, producers, engineers, songwriters and more.
10. Full lifetime membership to the NFT music group
11. Music distribution
12. Professional mix and mastering
13. Music marketing
14. Raffles
15. Community giveaways
16. Creative and commercial rights
17. Bands community
18. DJs community
19. Audio creators community
20. Future perks

As well as inclusion in the record label and more. 

Future updates and perks will be also be revealed soon as well as many other benefits in our roadmap & beyond.

OUR GOAL
Our goal is to rebuild the music industry.

OUR FOCUS
Our focus is to shift power to artist as the music business evolves.

WHY SUPPORT NFT MUSIC GROUP?
Supporting us help's artists create new possibilities and experiences with their fans.
All purchases goes back to the NFT music community.

Musicians are continuing to be creative with what they offer to their fan bases. 
Help us completely revolutionize the music industry like how the internet did.


PRICING AND RELEASE
There will only be 50.000 NFT Music Group memberships given away total. 
NFT Music Group Ethereum Piece are starting at Ξ 0.01, and will get exponentially more expensive as more are uploaded onto the OpenSea.
Be quick before they are all gone and purchase your membership while prices are low!!!
